#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:72
msgid ""
"The antiquated SDL 1.2 library our engine used has been replaced with the "
"much-improved SDL 2.0. This addresses many longstanding issues with OS and "
"hardware compatibility. In particular, support for fullscreen on multi-"
"monitor configurations is greatly improved, and various annoying mouse-"
"related issues on Apple Retina devices have been fixed."
msgstr ""
"我们的引擎曾经使用的过时的SDL 1.2库已被改进很多的SDL 2.0取代。这一改进解决了"
"很多长期存在的操作系统以及硬件兼容性问题。尤其是，多显示器系统上的全屏支持改"
"进很大，而Apple视网膜设备上与鼠标有关的很多恼人的问题也被修正了。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:74
msgid ""
"The user interface has also been further refined and polished. The main menu "
"now features a crisper 4K resolution background and a brand-new main theme "
"from composer <a href=\"http://mattiaswestlund.net/\">Mattias Westlund</a> "
"(West). Larger and crisper new fonts coupled with simplified dialog borders "
"and buttons enhance the game’s readability across a variety of hardware and "
"contexts, providing a more modern look. The add-ons manager, multiplayer "
"lobby, and game set-up interfaces have been completely revamped with fresh "
"designs that address many long-standing deficiencies in each. The "
"preferences dialog has also been through a substantial overhaul making it "
"easier to navigate and use."
msgstr ""
"用户界面得到了进一步的优化和打磨。主菜单界面中现在有了清晰的4K分辨率的背景"
"图，以及由作曲家<a href=\"http://mattiaswestlund.net/\">Mattias Westlund</"
"a>（West）所谱写的全新主题曲。更大、更清晰的字体以及简化的对话框边框及按钮，"
"让游戏界面的可读性在多种硬件上和上下文中都得到了增强，视觉效果也就更现代化"
"了。附加组件管理器、多人游戏大厅以及多人游戏参数配置界面已被全新设计完全取"
"代。新设计解决了这些界面上诸多长期存在的缺陷。首选项对话框也经过了充分的翻"
"新，变得更易于浏览和使用。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:76
msgid ""
"A plethora of units such as the Heavy Infantryman, Elvish Sylph, and Rogue "
"have received new animations and baseframes to bring them up to higher "
"quality standards and make the battlefield more lively and dynamic. New "
"generic portraits are available for several units too, including the Troll, "
"Ancient Wose, Walking Corpse, and Yeti. Finally, a <em>huge</em> number of "
"new terrains have been added to the game to enhance new and existing maps — "
"especially those set indoors and underground — and water and lava have been "
"redone in a new, fluid and fully-animated, aesthetically-pleasing style. "
"Many village types have also received time-of-day variations and will now "
"immersively light up when night falls."
msgstr ""
"大量单位，例如重装步兵、青空仙灵以及飞贼等获得了新的动画和基础帧，以将他们提"
"升至更高的质量标准，并让战场更加生动而富有活力。有几个单位，包括巨魔、上古树"
"人、行尸和雪人等，现在也有了新的通用立绘可用。最后，游戏中新增了<em>巨量</em>"
"的新地形，以增强新的和已有的地图——尤其是设定在室内和地下的——而水体和岩浆也使"
"用崭新的有完整流畅动画而很符合审美的风格重制了。很多类型的村庄也有了根据时段"
"变化的变体，如今当夜幕降临时，它们会沉浸在点亮的灯光中。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:78
msgid ""
"Finally, the in-game sounds for many units and user interface elements have "
"been replaced."
msgstr "最后，很多单位和用户界面元素所使用的游戏内声效也被替换了。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><h4>
#: template.html:80
msgid "Campaigns"
msgstr "战役"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><div><a>
#: template.html:82
msgid "<a href=\"images/start-3.jpg\">"
msgstr "<a href=\"images/start-3.jpg\">"

#. type: Attribute 'alt' of: <html><body><div><div><div><a><img>
#: template.html:82
msgid "Campaigns menu screenshot"
msgstr "战役菜单截屏"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:84
msgid ""
"The main campaign line-up welcomes the addition of <cite>Secrets of the "
"Ancients</cite>, a player-created campaign brought to you by the author of "
"<cite>Dead Water</cite>! Follow Ardonna of Tarrynth as she unearths the "
"secrets of the ancient lich-lords of the Green Isle in her search for "
"immortality."
msgstr ""
"主线战役迎来了<cite>古人之密</cite>的加入，这是由<cite>死水</cite>的作者为您"
"带来的玩家自制战役！跟随塔林斯的阿冬娜走上寻求永生的旅途，揭开绿岛上的上古巫"
"妖领主们的秘密。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><div><div><a>
#: template.html:87
msgid "<a href=\"images/start-4.jpg\">"
msgstr "<a href=\"images/start-4.jpg\">"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:90
msgid ""
"After years of technical setbacks, <cite>Under the Burning Suns</cite> "
"finally sees the desert elves faction completely revamped with brand-new "
"sprites, stunning new portraits by long-time contributing artist <a href="
"\"https://www.theartysquid.com/\">Emilien Rotival</a> (LordBob), and "
"revamped unit advancement trees with unique stats to further set them apart "
"from the standard forest elves featured throughout the rest of the game."
msgstr ""
"经历了好几年的技术性挫折之后，<cite>灼热双日之下</cite>中的沙漠精灵派系终于重"
"制了，用上了由长期美术贡献者<a href=\"https://www.theartysquid.com/"
"\">Emilien Rotival</a> （LordBob）所绘制的全新小人图和超棒的立绘。而单位升级"
"树也重制了，有了独特的数值，这让他们与游戏其他部分中重点表现的标准的森林精灵"
"的区别更大了。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:92
msgid ""
"<cite>Northern Rebirth’s</cite> first nine scenarios now have new and "
"improved maps, making use of new terrains and simpler, more organic designs. "
"The scenarios themselves have also been tweaked for more streamlined play. "
"<cite>Descent into Darkness</cite> received similar treatment with visual "
"improvements of its own."
msgstr ""
"<cite>北国重生</cite>的钱九个场景现在有了新的改进过的地图，使用了新地形和更简"
"洁、更有组织性的设计。而场景本身也有所调整，让游玩更加顺畅。<cite>堕入黑暗</"
"cite>也得到了类似待遇，并获得了独有的视效改进。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:94
msgid ""
"Because of the sheer number of singleplayer campaigns included in "
"<cite>Wesnoth</cite>, it has become increasingly difficult to get a sense of "
"the in-universe chronology of the stories they tell. To address this, the "
"Campaigns menu now provides the option to sort campaigns according to their "
"position in the timeline of Irdya’s history, as well as the option to sort "
"them alphabetically should one so desire."
msgstr ""
"<cite>韦诺</cite>中包含的单人战役数量很多，因此要在游戏世界内理清这些战役所讲"
"的故事的时间顺序变得越来越难了。为了解决这个问题，战役菜单中现在提供了将战役"
"按照其在伊迪亚的历史时间线上的位置来排序的选项，同时，也提供了按照战役名称的"
"字母顺序来排序，如果您希望如此的话便可以使用。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:96
msgid ""
"For those who wish to enrich their gameplay with player-made gimmicks or "
"challenges, it is now possible to use Modifications in singleplayer as well "
"as multiplayer. And should the temptation to reload saves in search of more "
"favorable outcomes overcome players, the new Deterministic Mode option will "
"keep them in check."
msgstr ""
"希望使用玩家自制的噱头和挑战来让游玩过程更加丰富多彩的玩家们，现在不论在多人"
"游戏还是单人游戏中都可以使用模组了。又及，要是玩家们被不断读档以得到更好结果"
"的诱惑给压倒的话，新的确定性模式可以约束他们。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><h4>
#: template.html:98
msgid "Multiplayer"
msgstr "多人游戏"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><div><a>
#: template.html:100
msgid "<a href=\"images/start-5.jpg\">"
msgstr "<a href=\"images/start-5.jpg\">"

#. type: Attribute 'alt' of: <html><body><div><div><div><a><img>
#: template.html:100
msgid "Multiplayer game setup screenshot"
msgstr "多人游戏设置截屏"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:102
msgid ""
"<cite>Wesnoth’s</cite> multiplayer lobby has been redesigned from the ground "
"up to provide a simpler experience for new players getting the hang of the "
"game. New features include clickable chat log links, separate tabs for "
"private message exchanges, easier filtering of games and players, faster "
"game creation for those using map authors’ recommended settings, and a more "
"comprehensive display of faction attributes."
msgstr ""
"<cite>韦诺</cite>的多人游戏大厅已从头全新设计，为正在熟悉游戏的新玩家提供了更"
"简单的体验。新功能包括可点击的聊天日志链接，用于私人消息交换的单独选项卡，更"
"简单的游戏和玩家过滤，为使用地图作者推荐设置的玩家提供的更快的游戏创建，以及"
"更全面的派系属性显示。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:104
msgid ""
"In terms of new content, players will be glad to know that the game’s roster "
"has been expanded with no fewer than <b>nine</b> community-contributed maps! "
"<cite>Wesnoth</cite> now ships with a total of 55 carefully-balanced maps "
"with many different environments and team set-ups for players to choose from."
msgstr ""
"在新内容方面，诸位玩家会很乐意知晓，游戏的地图花名册中新增了<b>九</b>张社区贡"
"献的地图！<cite>韦诺</cite>现在总共提供了55张经过精心平衡的地图，其中有许多不"
"同的环境和团队设置供玩家选择。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:106
msgid ""
"The Khalifate multiplayer faction introduced in version 1.12 has been "
"renamed the Dunefolk. This is part of an ongoing effort to expand their lore "
"and better integrate them into the world of Irdya. Accompanying this are a "
"multitude of stats changes to various Dunefolk units aimed to better balance "
"the faction in multiplayer matchups."
msgstr ""
"版本1.12中引入的哈里发多人游戏派别已更名为沙丘游民。我们正在进行扩充沙丘游民"
"的相关设定并更好地将他们融入伊迪亚世界的努力，而这次更名是这一努力的一部分。"
"伴随这次更名而来的，是各个沙丘游民单位的大量属性数据变化。其目的是更好地平衡"
"多人对决中的各个派系。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:108
msgid ""
"It is now possible to forfeit a multiplayer game, signaling that you no "
"longer intend to keep playing without simply suddenly quitting."
msgstr ""
"现在在多人游戏中可以放弃了，这允许你在不突然退出的情况下，表明不再继续游玩的"
"意愿。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><h4>
#: template.html:110
msgid "General"
msgstr "总体改进"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><div><div><a>
#: template.html:113
msgid "<a href=\"images/start-6.jpg\">"
msgstr "<a href=\"images/start-6.jpg\">"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:116
msgid ""
"It is now possible to customize the colors of the movement/attack orbs "
"displayed alongside units on the map to make it easier for players with "
"different color perception to identify each unit’s status. An option "
"(disabled by default) is also provided to display a color orb on enemy units."
msgstr ""
"现在可以自定义地图上单位旁边显示的移动/攻击球的颜色，以便具有不同的色彩感知能"
"力的玩家能够更轻松地识别每个单位的状态。游戏中还提供了一个选项（默认情况下禁"
"用），用于在敌方单位之上显示颜色球。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:118
msgid ""
"Switching to another application while <cite>Wesnoth</cite> is running now "
"pauses the music by default. If you’d prefer it to keep playing, there is an "
"option for that."
msgstr ""
"现在，当在<cite>韦诺</cite> 运行中切换到另一个应用程序时，默认情况下将暂停音"
"乐。如果您更喜欢继续播放的话，那么有一个选项可用。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:120
msgid ""
"In order for players to more easily include details about their system when "
"reporting issues with the game, a brand new version information dialog is "
"accessible from the bottom-left corner of the main menu. Among the "
"information it provides are the operating system version, paths to the "
"various files <cite>Wesnoth</cite> uses, the version numbers of the code "
"libraries the game is built against, and a list of optional features enabled "
"by the packager."
msgstr ""
"为了让玩家在报告游戏问题时可以更容易地在报告中包含包含其系统的详细信息，现在"
"玩家可以通过主菜单的左下角来访问全新的版本信息对话框。它提供的信息包括操作系"
"统版本、<cite>韦诺</cite> 使用的各种文件的路径、游戏在构建时所针对的各个代码"
"库的版本号，以及打包者所启用的可选功能的列表。"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:122
msgid ""
"Finally, for Windows players, the game’s configuration, saves, and add-ons "
"are now always stored in their Documents folder. This change was made to "
"avoid various issues inherent to the legacy approach of writing to the "
"system’s Program Files folder, which is neither recommended nor well-"
"supported on newer Windows versions. Note that while the legacy option of "
"storing said files in the game’s installation path is gone, that behavior "
"may still be achieved through the use of certain command-line options for "
"those who prefer to install <cite>Wesnoth</cite> on an external drive."
msgstr ""
"最后，对于Windows玩家而言，游戏的配置、存档和附加组件现在始终存储在其 \"文档"
"\" 文件夹中。进行此更改是为了避免遗留的“写入系统的Program Files文件夹”这一方"
"法所固有的各种问题。较新的Windows版本既不推荐也不能很好地支持这种方法。请注"
"意，虽然“在游戏的安装路径中存储上述文件”的旧选项已经消失，但那些喜欢在外部驱"
"动器上安装<cite>韦诺</cite>的用户, 仍可通过使用某些命令行选项来实现此行为。"

